P & U gets nod in Sweden for Nicorette tablets . Swedish / U . S . drugs company Pharmacia & Upjohn said on Wednesday that Sweden ' s drug authorities had approved the company ' s Nicorette tablets that are used to help people give up smoking . P & U said in a statement that Nicorette tablets would be launched in Sweden in the second half of 1997 and would be sold over - the - counter , prescription free . P & U said Nicorette products are also available in the form of chewing gum , plaster , inhaler and nasal spray . 
